# Session handoff documents (ephemeral, not source)
*HANDOFF*.md
*Handoff*.md
*handoff*.md
"1 # Career-Ops Session Handoff*"
"Master Career-Ops Build.MD"
career_ops_handoff_pipeline.md

# Large data files (scan-history already listed above, embeddings are binary)
data/embeddings/

# Pipeline / hygiene one-off backups (regenerate anytime)
**/*.bak

# Claude Code task state (local only)
.claude/task-manifest.json
data/scan-scheduler.log

# Append-only automation telemetry (local machine; dashboard reads last lines)
data/events/*.jsonl
!data/events/.gitkeep

# Scanner-generated research / prefilter output (2,292+ .md files)
# Gitignored 2026-04-17: these dirs churn constantly from background scans
# and dominated the working tree. Files stay on disk; only git stops tracking.
# Template files like _queue.txt remain tracked; only .md output is ignored.
# Research notes that need to be shared should live elsewhere (e.g., docs/).
data/company-intel/*.md
!data/company-intel/.gitkeep
data/prefilter-results/*.md
!data/prefilter-results/.gitkeep
